    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Typefaces that are within the large class of roman style typefaces and are the more upright, nonitalic characters. For the large class of roman typefaces, use "roman (typeface style group)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
